<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/555359-should-californians-who-are-running-out">Should Californians, who are running out of water along with Nevada, Arizona, and New Mexico, start charging unsupported water users who are new to the state a large fee for the additional strain they are placing on the state&#39;s natural resources? 

What else might be done?</a>
</div>
