<div class='communityQuestionAndAnswer'>
<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/590758-just-in-reading-your-response-the-term">Just in reading your response, the term &quot;marginal user&quot; sounds like individual people, and that the retail/commercial user sounds like a cartel could move in? Nestle taking a towns water comes to mind as an example. I may just be off the wall, or I may be voicing a fear that could become reality. The West is a marginal environment that we have recklessly over-populated.</a>
</div>
