This answer contains spoilers…
<span class='spoilerAnswerText'>
<a class="jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction">(view spoiler)</a><span class="spoilerContainer" style="display: none">[
  
    I agree with your assessment regarding commercial users, especially like Nestlé. When a corporation profits from the natural resource, they should pay<a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">…more</a>
    I agree with your assessment regarding commercial users, especially like Nestlé. When a corporation profits from the natural resource, they should pay a greater user fee. Individuals/families should pay less based on survival use. Homeowners’ use might be apportioned based on uses, i.e.: swimming pools, etc. Your phrase “recklessly overpopulated” is truth, when water is piped over mountains taking water from other desert states. <a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">(less)</a>
  
 <a class="jsHideSpoiler spoilerAction">(hide spoiler)</a>]</span>
</span>
</div>
