<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/41883929-the-dreamt-land"><img alt="The Dreamt Land: Chasing Water and Dust Across California" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1552656023l/41883929._SX98_.jpg" />
